-- McCarthy & Stone to Sell Financial Services, Sunday Times Says
-- B y   L i n d s a y   F o r t a d o
-- 2012-07-01T07:30:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-01/mccarthy-stone-to-sell-financial-services-sunday-times-says.html
McCarthy & Stone Plc, a British
retirement home developer, will sell financial services targeted
to people over 50, the Sunday Times reported, citing Ali
Crossley, who was hired by the company to lead the project.  Its products will include pension annuities advice, funeral
planning and equity annuities advice, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lindsay Fortado in London at 
 lfortado@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at   aaarons@bloomberg.net . 